    <scopecontent>
      <head>Collection Overview</head>
      <p>This collection consists of a large scrapbook and a box with file folders. The scrap
                book includes over 200 pages of items relating to Wesleyan’s centennial, including
                badges, pamphlets, newspaper clippings, menus, playbills, and more. The scrapbook is
                organized into categories, including sections entirely of newspaper clippings and
                one page with attached alumni and event worker badges, for example. The file folders
                contain large photographs, as well as copies of similar paper items to those
                contained in the scrapbook. They also contain correspondence, including telegrams
                and typed letters regarding the events. </p>
    </scopecontent>
